content:
InheritanceLevel Enum

Definition

Defines identifiers for types of inheritance levels.

In this Article

public enum InheritanceLevel
Inheritance
Object
ValueType
System.Enum
InheritanceLevel

Remarks

InheritanceLevel defines identifiers for numeric IDs that are used with the InheritanceAttribute attribute to indicate various levels of inheritance.

Fields

Inherited

The object is inherited.
InheritedReadOnly

The object is inherited, but has read-only access.
NotInherited

The object is not inherited.
